Mary's Murder Story


1. Found in her penthouse. She had a note written on her body in ink
2. There was a ring found at the scene of the crime
3. Find out that it was the ring she gave to her boyfriend
4. Find a picture of him with the ring on
5. A witness saw Janette go into the penthouse the night she was murdered and heard a scream (turns out it was a bug)
6. Kate was very upset that she wasnt appointed to the CEO (Younger than mary), So furious that she didnt come to her celebratory party
7. Robert and mary broke up over money dispute. Teamed up with kate because she promised to give him money after she got het new position 
